dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: nahiyatay Ali al-Gharbi wa Shaykh Sa'd
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Misaha al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Ali al-Gharbi and Shaykh Sa'd section.] Alternate title: Liwa' al-'Amarah: qada' Ali al-Gharbi: nahiyaayt Ali al-Ghabri was Shaykh Sa'd. [ Al-Amarah province: Ali al-Gharbi district: Shaykh Sa'd and Ali al-Gharbi sections.] Relief shown by hachures and form lines. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed 1931-1939.Tribal lands and land ownership are shown.
